      <h1>Funding Plan</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Make a realistic budget so the team knows what it costs to start, build, and compete.</p>
      <section class="content-section">
        <p>A good funding plan helps the team avoid surprises. Start with the basic costs, then add a buffer for tools, replacement parts, and travel.</p>
        <div class="content-subsection">
          <h3>Common budget items</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>FIRST registration and event fees</li>
            <li>Robot kit, electronics, and spare parts</li>
            <li>Tools, storage, and workspace supplies</li>
            <li>Travel, uniforms, and team outreach materials</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Action:</strong> Draft a budget sheet and decide which expenses need sponsor support, fundraising, or donations.</p>
      </section>
